Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:32.73,Main,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,Darkness will consume you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:34.64,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:37.21,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'll find One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:41.98,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,and become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:39.84,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.44,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:51.15,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one who ever conquered that ocean\Nwas the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:57.61,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has killed\Nthe dreams and ambitions of countless pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:03.32,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:07.12,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:11.42,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.81,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,In order to defeat one of the Four Emperors, rulers of the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:21.59,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew\Nformed a Pirate Alliance with Trafalgar Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:25.47,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now they've invaded Dress Rosa\Nin order to release Caesar to Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:32.73,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Luffy learned that the prize of the colosseum battle\Ntournament was the Mera Mera Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:38.16,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,and decided to join the fight, competing against mighty foes from all over the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.83,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,All this because of one punch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:45.66,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He hit me in the head more times than I can count!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:49.58,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,I'll shatter every bone in your body to dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.57,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,Eight Impact Fist Secret Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.46,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.09,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Thor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.62,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,Non-Drilling Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:03.51,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.09,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,Non-Drilling Nail!{Xemnas: Wouldn't it's strength increase if he were to spin?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:30.50,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,What a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:37.01,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,The victor of Block C's fierce battle royale, who just defeated a legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.96,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,is Lucy the Gladiator!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.78,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.75,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,The battle royale at Corrida Colosseum continues!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:08.70,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Currently, three fighters have won\Nthe right to challenge the Donquixote Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:20.41,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,The victor of Block A,\Nthe Blackbeard Pirates' "Champion", Jesus Burgess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:33.27,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,From Block B we have the captain\Nof the Barto Club Pirates, Bartolomeo the Cannibal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.77,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,And from Block C...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:43.82,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Our very own gladiator, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.43,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Only one more finalist remains to be selected!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:53.77,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,However,\Ndue to the massive damage done to the arena,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:58.21,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,we will postpone the start of Block D\Nfor fifteen minutes! { def: yeah, 15 minutes should take care of that }{Xemnas: Magic?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.38,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Bring out a replacement arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.67,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Fix it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:06.23,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Please be patient until the Block D fight begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.29,Main,Cavendish,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.03,Main,Cavendish,0,0,0,,There's nowhere for you to run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.02,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Cabbage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.10,Main,Cavendish,0,0,0,,Durandal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.70,Main,Cavendish,0,0,0,,Stand still!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.47,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:36.07,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Cavendish's lost it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:41.17,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,That lowlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.38,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.38,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,He shouted "Straw Hat" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.47,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:51.36,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Wasn't he that pirate who {\i1}failed{\i0}\Nto save his brother at Marineford?{Yeah they say "choujou sensou", which we have always translated as "the great war" here... but over time I have grown to not particularly like that translation at all so I prefer to just say Marineford personally. They both get the point across anyway. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:57.48,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,As if {\i1}not{\i0}{\fscx130} {\r}saving someone is special!  I can do that too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:04.61,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,W-W-Whad're you doin'?!  Cut i' out! {Note that due to being kinda flattened by a barrier he's having some trouble enunciating clearly. Hence the "doin'". If possible, plz add some more indicators of this. -Starfish}{ def: changing t to d represents it well but makes a bit tough to read.  just went with i' instead of it }
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:08.11,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,I am a noble from the Kingdom of Biggschots! {Yeah I just copied FUNi's translation of the place here. It's originally "Doereena Oukoku" which translates to something like "Super-Great Kingdom". -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:10.82,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:14.25,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,You're crushing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:18.00,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea who you were just casually laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:29.82,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Now listen up!  Straw Hat Luffy-senpai is the man\Nwho will someday stand at the very top of this era!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:32.71,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,He is the future Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.59,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I was there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.57,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,on that fateful day, over two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:48.21,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,It was Loguetown in East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:53.19,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,On the legendary execution stand,\Nwhere the Pirate King Roger himself died!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:56.42,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Trapped in a hopeless position, that man declared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:08:00.78,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm the man who will be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.97,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,And in that moment, the heavens...{Xemnas: Never knew Dragon lived in the heavens. No wonder no one can find him.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:31.77,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,...brought down the lightning, and saved him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:46.33,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,I survived after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.44,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.38,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I witnessed a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:09:00.09,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Ever since that day, I fanatically read\Neverything I could about the Straw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:04.94,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Alabasta, Enies Lobby, Impel Down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:09.83,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,And last but not least,\Nthe fateful events at Marineford!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.83,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,That incident sent shivers down my spine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:21.70,Flashbacks,Dude,0,0,0,,Boss!  What should we do\Nwith the enemy soldiers we just defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.70,Flashbacks,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Just throw'em in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:30.90,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Back where I lived, I was just a crimelord who's turf covered a measly one hundred and fifty towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.26,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I looked up to Luffy-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.68,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,And finally, I set out to sea myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:54.01,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Just {\i1}try{\i0}{\fscx130} {\r}to say something like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:10:00.54,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,You put your pathetic existence on a pedestal,\Nand act like you're looking down on Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.95,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Did I hear that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:10.89,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,What can you do?  You pathetic insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.61,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Now Bartolomeo's gone crazy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:22.68,Main,Cavendish,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:24.27,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.36,Main,Cavendish,0,0,0,,I said let go, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:36.56,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Why should I have to fight you in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:38.43,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.60,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Hey!  Somebody stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:58.49,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,I'm not getting involved!  It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.97,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, there's no way I could go up to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.92,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I'm chickening out and losing my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.77,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I'm just too nervous to approach him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:10.43,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,That scar underneath his eye... He's the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:12.69,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,He's so friggin' cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:15.85,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Huh?  My eyes are tearing up so much I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:22.23,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,How I wish I could kill that filthy cabbage\Nand protect my hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.43,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Hey you!  Gedh awah fwom him, cab...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.20,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,It's no good, I almost bit my tongue off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.84,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:43.80,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,Listen up!\NGramps has something he wants to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.82,Main,Boo,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:50.43,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Huh?  You're still doing this?!  Look, I won fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.69,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:06.03,Thoughts,Chinjao,0,0,0,,I don't even hate Garp any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:10.24,Thoughts,Chinjao,0,0,0,,I want to convey my immense gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.68,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,Please, just let me thank...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.84,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,Wait, grandson of Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.39,Main,Cavendish,0,0,0,,Hold it, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.06,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,He ran straight past me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:27.10,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Um, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.23,Main,Cavendish,0,0,0,,Hey, don't run away from a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.52,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,W-W-W-What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:37.24,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I wanna talk to him, but I just don't know how!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.90,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:42.44,Thoughts,Chinjao,0,0,0,,I wanted to show my gratitude\Nfor putting my head back to normal... {kind of guessing on what's thoughts and what's not here -Fadey}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:46.26,Thoughts,Chinjao,0,0,0,,by offering to make \Nmy grandchildren's Happou Navy serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.74,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:52.85,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What is with all these guys?  They're so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.55,Main,Chinjao,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:56.59,Secondary,Cavendish,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.59,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:09.32,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Really... I just want to relax for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.81,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,This way, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:15.51,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you!  Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:18.35,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,It's Rebecca.  You sure have a lot of enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.08,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.48,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Right, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:29.83,Main,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,Well, you could say the same about Shiliew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:55.25,Main,Burgess,0,0,0,,But I don't trust Aokiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:01.98,Main,Burgess,0,0,0,,Oh, hold on, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.60,Main,Burgess,0,0,0,,Straw Hat's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:12.12,Main,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,Oh, you're there too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:14.93,Main,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:20.98,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.26,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,So you're...{Copy-paste from 446... DAMN we've been doing this for a long time =| -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.67,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,Blackbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.35,Flashbacks,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:38.98,Flashbacks,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,I sure was surprised when I heard that you were Commander Ace's little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:41.47,Flashbacks,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:43.27,Flashbacks,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,They're gonna start soon, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.59,Flashbacks,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,Your brother's execution, that is!{End copy-paste from 446... DAMN we've been doing this for a long time =| -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:53.70,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Blackbeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:58.11,Main,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,That's right.  It's been a while, hasn't it? { def: if he says the same thing as the flashback then we should keep the line the same }
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:03.96,Main,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,So I understand you're participating in the tournament, "Lucy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:09.66,Main,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,But my man, Burgess,\Nis going to win the Mera Mera Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:16.95,Main,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,It's almost like Ace is joining my crew.\NIt's going to be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:21.09,Main,Blackbeard,0,0,0,,I mean, he refused the offer last time, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:30.81,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You're the last person I'd let have Ace's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:43.25,Main,Burgess,0,0,0,,I look forward to fighting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:55.97,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.28,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:01.53,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:07.69,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,You know that pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.95,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:10.98,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I can't let him win the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.33,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Don't you have any more free samples, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.92,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,You're just going to eat samples\Nwithout buying anything, aren't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.60,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.31,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:32.20,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,What do you want, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:35.23,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You're gonna buy me food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:38.18,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Oh, he's a friend of yours, Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.89,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.98,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:53.65,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm digging in! {I do intensely dislike trying to come up with natural ways to translate "itadakimasu"... -Starfish}{ def: rub a dub dub, thanks for the grub. }
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:58.91,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Sorry I couldn't afford much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:03.98,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Don't worry.  Thanks for treating me, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.57,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,So, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:11.58,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,This is the dormitory for the colosseum gladiators.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:15.25,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Though some people would call it a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:27.75,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Guest competitors never come down here, so you can relax here until the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:32.09,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Really?  That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.53,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,That was some fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.99,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,You're a lot stronger than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.54,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:50.75,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yup.  The colosseum-lunch is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:59.22,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You're not hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:04.64,Flashbacks,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Mother, I'm hungry.{Xemnas: I don't think a child would use the word famished.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:09.07,Flashbacks,Scarlett,0,0,0,,I know.  We haven't had anything to eat for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:14.54,Flashbacks,Scarlett,0,0,0,,Rebecca,\Ncan you manage on your own for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:24.29,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,No, I... I don't get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:29.29,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Really?  You're like a samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:35.71,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Got you!  Rebecca, this is your chance to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.76,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.80,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Isn't that why you brought him down here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:41.43,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on here, Rebecca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.32,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:52.45,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,H-Hey!  You'll spill the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:53.57,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.83,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:58.25,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,You have to kill him,\Nor you'll never accomplish your goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.11,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:54.18,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Rebecca was pinned!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:56.14,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,I can't believe he moves faster than she does!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.65,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.19,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,I deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:14.44,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do anything\Nto the person who bought me lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.73,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,I tried to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.96,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.  I'm not dead. {Xemnas: Nuance and all.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:22.82,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Besides, you weren't really trying to kill me. { def: you weren't really trying to kill me }{Xemnas: Definitely prefer your suggestion.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.72,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Ow... { def: This hurts. }
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:27.73,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,How could he forgive you so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:31.96,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,That really shows the difference in power\Nbetween you two, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:41.80,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,We would've had a little hope, at least,\Nif we'd been able to take out one of the big shots here.{Xemnas: Not sure if he's referring to all of them or just Rebecca, as going by their bandages, they've already participated and lost, and thus have no hope of winning anyway.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:43.55,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,A mummy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.47,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,We're not mummies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:49.45,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,We're the prisoner gladiators.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.97,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Rebecca is one of us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:56.76,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,We have to keep fighting in the arena\Nuntil we're killed for the amusement of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:21:01.07,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,All because we showed some slight resistance toward the Doflamingo Family. { def: we didn't support the Doflamingo Family with enough enthusiasm }
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:08.44,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,The king says we can earn our freedom by winning a thousand matches...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:12.54,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,but even the most talented fighter would lose if\Nhe was forced to fight to the death a thousand times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:17.38,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,And anyone who tries to escape is shot to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.31,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,There's no way out for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:30.51,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,Ten years ago, before Doflamingo became king,\Ncolosseum battles weren't fought to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:37.74,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,But under his rule, the country has become sharply divided between light and shadow.{Xemnas: Spelling fix}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:45.65,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:51.98,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,will win the tournament today, whatever it takes... {Quality... POWER UUUUPP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:58.25,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,and use the Mera Mera Fruit's power\Nto kill Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:09.44,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Today, Soldier-san's army\Nis going to challenge Doflamingo... {Her waist is smaller than Nami's here... seriously, she looks like a concentration camp victim O_O}{Xemnas: Well considering she's a prisoner, and I doubt she gets much money if any at all, I don't think she's fed properly.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:15.93,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,in order to free us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:21.27,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,He intends to sacrifice his own life...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:23.44,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,to bring down this kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:25.69,Flashbacks,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:31.12,Flashbacks,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Soldier-san is valiant...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:33.39,Flashbacks,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,and he will always watch over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:43.42,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,I will do it before he can!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:49.83,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,I'm tired of always being protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:59.89,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,This time, I'm going to protect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:12.20,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,One night, a great tragedy befell Dress Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:20.37,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Rebecca lost everyone she loved, and lived\Nthrough her cruel fate with a one-legged soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:24.92,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The story behind their strong bond is revealed at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:26.17,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:27.42,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I will Protect You!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:29.31,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Rebecca and the One-Legged Soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.31,0:23:31.52,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
